<p><strong>英雄联盟2020全球总决赛冠亚军决赛收视破纪录</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201211/7c3319c85a2d43c097d9a94d3bd3b8b9.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
